body:
## Volgenmodel
https://github.com/CAIsr/volgenmodel

volgenmodel creates nonlinear models from a series of input MINC files - modelling was originally created as part of the ANDI project funded by DCRC




## Volgenmodel-nipype
https://github.com/CAIsr/volgenmodel-nipype

volgenmodel-nipype is the port of volgenmodel to nipype. It creates nonlinear models from a series of input MINC files.
